{"tid":548378,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳 業 坤 搭 港 鐵 女 粉 護 送 返 歸","createTime":"2018-02-02T12:59:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-02T15:53:04.000Z","uid":35964,"like":3,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"428bf704f6f809308b793eb95530930c641b8eb7","tid":548378,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T12:59:55.000Z","msg":"歌手吳業坤於剛過去的樂壇頒獎禮上成績不及往年，但獲得一班忠實粉絲支持，向來夠「貼地」的他日前工作後搭港鐵返歸，全程有三名女粉絲「陪搭」並從旁鼓勵。<br />\n<br />\n參加歌唱比賽入行的吳業坤，過去兩年狀態大勇，在多個頒獎禮獲得歌曲獎外，更冧莊「我最喜愛的男歌手」獎，人氣急升，工作接踵而來，身價亦三級跳。一向慳家的他，去年還花約50萬元購買新車代步。不過，近年他專注拍劇，忽略了音樂創作，於剛過去的樂壇頒獎禮成績不及往年，但仍有不少紛絲支持。<br />\n<br />\n日前下午，坤坤在銅鑼灣出席活動後，被大批粉絲圍着傾偈，沒有架子的他與粉絲邊行邊傾，期間有途人認出並要求合照，他亦來者不拒。其中有三名女粉絲更充當助手，陪「貼地」的坤坤搭港鐵。<br />\n<br />\n笠罩入閘<br />\n為免過分張揚，坤坤進入港鐵站後即戴上口罩，幾位忠粉一直陪伴在側，護送他落車返歸。<br />\n<br />\n另一日，坤坤前往電台工作，同樣有數名男女粉絲到場守候，當他工作後步出大門，粉絲即上前寒暄及安慰，坤坤亦識做地跟他們合照，其後才獨自乘七人車離開。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20180122/photo/0122-00282-029b1.jpg?t=1517576295870\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180122%2Fphoto%2F0122-00282-029b1.jpg%3Ft%3D1517576295870&h=16d211e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20180122/photo/0122-00282-029b2.jpg?t=1517576300087\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180122%2Fphoto%2F0122-00282-029b2.jpg%3Ft%3D1517576300087&h=e714b506&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20180122/photo/0122-00282-029b3.jpg?t=1517576304225\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180122%2Fphoto%2F0122-00282-029b3.jpg%3Ft%3D1517576304225&h=3f0f8513&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20180122/photo/0122-00282-029b4.jpg?t=1517576308002\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180122%2Fphoto%2F0122-00282-029b4.jpg%3Ft%3D1517576308002&h=636812c2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d973bdf5a928d43a92543051cd7b388eb8ce3b2a","tid":548378,"uid":31920,"like":20,"dislike":2,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T13:03:02.000Z","msg":"戴口罩做乜撚<br />\n佢唔係以為有人識佢呀？"},{"pid":"ffc7bca534549416abf9b9d98b34ac2d33be78d6","tid":548378,"uid":109163,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T13:04:44.000Z","msg":"個個粉絲都咁重量級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44f34eb0b972178b1bdbbf841c9aff3b75380c7c","tid":548378,"uid":15358,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T13:10:36.000Z","msg":"淨係請得起咁嘅質素？"},{"pid":"bf84991a33a008b8e38f27e340b380271d27a66c","tid":548378,"uid":21423,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T13:11:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba5d689b8a3652efefd3e8a544cac47954ba0101","tid":548378,"uid":129221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ffc7bca534549416abf9b9d98b34ac2d33be78d6","tid":548378,"uid":109163,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T13:04:44.000Z","msg":"個個粉絲都咁重量級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T13:14:06.000Z","msg":"證明無返咁上下係唔會識得欣賞人內涵<br />\n鍾意坤哥係成熟既表現"},{"pid":"74ea59aca45e60c3e02d848f9beb2941e9c2c7a6","tid":548378,"uid":35621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T13:21:19.000Z","msg":"d女比你溝曬啦"},{"pid":"b404d2f032c5f3030376c4eb037642c348dd880c","tid":548378,"uid":137627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T13:26:36.000Z","msg":"畢直唔夠暫時請得呢D"},{"pid":"63ae5e03264606602f728725fe6c981d17d1475c","tid":548378,"uid":163621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-02T13:29:42.000Z","msg":"成班c9阿叔，大台歌手粉絲都係呢啲<br />\n人地柏豪柏宇好多靚女fans"},{"pid":"2c37e1afa9e714948092fb2fd87745432409014d","tid":548378,"uid":149489,"like":0,"dislike":0